metadata.description:
The PHUNK FORCE 1 V2 is the final CryptoPhunks permissionless collaboration with Louis Vuitton & Nike designed by TEJI.

Each holder is entitled to anonymously claim 1x physical shoe free of charge via a short claim window in the official TEJIVERSE discord: https://discord.com/invite/TXtPXkWjSv
metadata.name: PHUNK FORCE 1 V2 by TEJI
